code: @Test public void testDefaultThreadPoolProfile() throws Exception {     CamelContext context = getMandatoryBean(CamelContext.class, "camel-D").     ThreadPoolProfile profile = context.getExecutorServiceManager().getDefaultThreadPoolProfile().     assertEquals(5, profile.getPoolSize().intValue()).     assertEquals(15, profile.getMaxPoolSize().intValue()).     assertEquals(25, profile.getKeepAliveTime().longValue()).     assertEquals(250, profile.getMaxQueueSize().intValue()).     assertEquals(ThreadPoolRejectedPolicy.Abort, profile.getRejectedPolicy()). }
